Billionaire II is a thrilling and exciting strategic business game where you can make real dollars. The main goal of the game is to become a sole owner of the Billionaire City. The game takes place in Billionaire City. Here you can purchase real estate and build a foundation of your future fortune. You can also raise loans, invest your capital in bonds at the stock market and even acquire your competitors businesses. This game is not just about luck. It requires shrewd planning and clever strategy; you gradually build up your fortune.
